Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's popularity slumps
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxll
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Mar 1979
President Carter losing support of both public and his own party. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.